///|
/// Yuegui — MoonBit-native static site generator.
///
/// Packages:
/// - `core` — pure content model, diagnostics, route/link validation
/// - `format_markdown` — Markdown parser and render adapter
/// - `format_typst` — Typst adapter (stub in MVP, experimental in Phase 2)
/// - `theme` — layout model, template engine, HTML renderer
/// - `runtime` — filesystem, process, file watcher, dev server
/// - `cli` — command parsing and user-facing output
